in part of Burma.

163
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,660
Is that true?

164
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:04,660
Yeah.

165
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:07,050
China has a very big influence,

166
00:09:07,050 --> 00:09:11,019
not only just one ethnic group but quite a
lot of

167
00:09:11,019 --> 00:09:14,899
different ethnic groups mostly along their
border so yeah.

168
00:09:14,899 --> 00:09:15,899
Definitely.

169
00:09:15,899 --> 00:09:18,300
They have a big influence and they have support

170
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,980
from some of those ethnic groups.

171
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:22,860
Can you tell me a little bit about what's
happening

172
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:24,339
with the militia groups in the Wa state

173
00:09:24,339 --> 00:09:26,350
along the border with China?

174
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:32,170
So the Wa state, it was a self-administrative
zone

175
00:09:32,170 --> 00:09:35,240
by constitution in Burma so it is part of
Burma,

176
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:40,339
it is Eastern part of Burma that borders China.

177
00:09:40,339 --> 00:09:44,540
And because they have this really long,

178
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,970
good relationship with China,

179
00:09:45,970 --> 00:09:49,910
later on they get the biggest support from
China

180
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:52,519
compared to many other ethnic groups in Burma

181
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:55,850
and later on this administrative region

182
00:09:55,850 --> 00:09:59,610
had become a part of China.

183
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:02,800
When you go to this area,

184
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:05,959
you will feel like you are in China because
the currency

185
00:10:05,959 --> 00:10:09,360
is in Chinese currency.

186
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:11,860
People are speaking mostly Chinese

187
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:13,649
and most people don't speak Burmese

188
00:10:13,649 --> 00:10:21,560
so they have this very identical Chinese influence

189
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:26,440
as well as the enormous support that they
have from China.

190
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:31,620
This area also had a large number of Chinese
investments

191
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:35,550
on the extractive industries drug-trade route

192
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:39,180
because this region also is quite close

193
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:41,310
to other Southeast Asian nations

194
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:44,649
so it's kind of on the border with other countries
as well

195
00:10:44,649 --> 00:10:50,680
so it's the perfect location for illicit drug-trade

196
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:53,350
and other sorts of investment.

197
00:10:53,350 --> 00:11:00,550
So the Chinese authority is basically supporting
this area

198
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:03,810
because of the investments and things like
that?

199
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:05,810
Not just because of the investment

200
00:11:05,810 --> 00:11:09,690
