which they can show against the Burmese authorities
as well.

207
00:11:30,589 --> 00:11:35,319
So it's a very strange way to describe this
area

208
00:11:35,319 --> 00:11:39,329
because it is Burma but it looks like China.

209
00:11:39,329 --> 00:11:44,470
So is this not a conflict with the Burmese
government

210
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:49,020
if China is essentially supporting this self-administrative

211
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:53,040
but kind of separatist state that then

212
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,279
they are able to have a lot of influence over?

213
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:56,279
Definitely.

214
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:59,640
So in the very beginning of this armed groups,

215
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:03,790
they will attack quite a lot by the central
Burmese army

216
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:08,139
but later on when they get support from China,

217
00:12:08,139 --> 00:12:13,250
they had the strongest armed forces among
any of the ethnic groups

218
00:12:13,250 --> 00:12:16,759
so the central Burmese government

219
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:19,829
don't usually try to provoke this particular
group.

220
00:12:19,829 --> 00:12:24,149
They feel like if they provoke this ethnic
group,

221
00:12:24,149 --> 00:12:27,149
it will look like they are provoking the Chinese
authority as well

222
00:12:27,149 --> 00:12:32,080
so that's just this very strange relationship
with this group,

223
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,090
with the central Burmese government.

224
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:38,790
That's interesting because with China,

225
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:40,160
a lot of what they talk about

226
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:43,470
is not interfering with other countries internal
affairs

227
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:44,500
because they don't want other countries

228
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:45,620
to interfere in their affairs

229
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:49,319
but then it seems that that is a pretty big
interference

230
00:12:49,319 --> 00:12:50,319
in Burma's affairs

231
00:12:50,319 --> 00:12:53,839
to kind of be supporting this other group.

232
00:12:53,839 --> 00:12:58,069
Well, China always make this kind of rules

233
00:12:58,069 --> 00:13:02,220
whenever they talk at the international level,

234
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:06,760
they say things only if they have interest.

235
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:14,379
They would tell the international organizations

236
00:13:14,379 --> 00:13:17,130
that "we don't interfere what's going on in
Burma"

